    "The density of the yellow circles coincides with the number of times that the corresponding change is recognised as constructive by human experts.",
    "Instead of optimising the movement of one specific player, TacticAI can recommend improvements for multiple players in one generation step through suggesting better positions to block the opposing players, or better orientations to track them more efficiently.",
